<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>KUM AA MER LENGMANGMI AH HIN PATHIAN CH454</title>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Kum aa mer lengmang mi ah hin Pathian, Kan in bochan, Kan i ruahchan
 mi le tihmi chungah, Na kut kan hmuh, Ni thar le zing thar hna an chuah
 sinin, Na zaang-fahnak, A thar in kan hmuh t han.

[V2]
 Maw kan Pathian nangmah na kut chungah, Kan caan a um, Zumhnak in
 Biakam mi Ram ah kan hruai, Lam kan hmuhsak, Nangmah he cun, muihnak hi a
 ceu ko, Zumhnak muithlam, Hmuhnak ah canter ko.

[V3]
 Hmailei kum caan zong a uktu Pathian, Nang kan in zulh,Kan thawn lioah
 Bawipa kan kal tak hlah, Kan umpi ko, Nifa kan nunnak changreu rung si
 law, Kan nunnak dih tik i kan inn si ko.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>454</hymn_number>
</song>